  "text": "The only question is, is there anything that we have done wrong, or anything that we could do to make the instrument more comfortable? We scan this instrument. This instrument has been much aided by these precautions. We suggest only some attention to the neck which seems in this body/distortion to be distorted in the area of strength/weakness. More support, therefore, to the neck area may be an aid.",
